{"tid":2133030,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"家居隔離女確診者離開太平花園　法團主席報警求助","createTime":"2020-07-30T18:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T00:50:10.000Z","uid":5195,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f6964b4c4002073534b80a657d49afe33089d194","tid":2133030,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T18:34:28.000Z","msg":"一名37歲女子在前日(29日)被確診感染新冠肺炎，其後在何文田太平道2號太平花園住所家居隔離。至昨日(31日)晚上11時45分，有保安員發現該名確診女子與男友外出，遂通知大廈立案法團主席報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n數名身穿全副防護裝束的警員登樓調查，惟事主所在的單位無人應門，警員無奈收隊離去，並追緝該名確診女子，保安員其後在大廈電梯大堂位置消毒。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，該名女患者於本月22日發燒入院其後出院，在前日(29日)被確診後等候入院，她並無外遊紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200731/photo/bkn-20200731005341345-0731_00822_001_04b.jpg?20200731020609\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200731%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200731005341345-0731_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20200731020609&h=9560182a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce26d4300203b32f632d07b947261e979265e9df","tid":2133030,"uid":88743,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T18:36:16.000Z","msg":"風向將會帶去禁足令/健康碼<br />\n之後無人屌林鄭唔封關<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa6037aac797d989cb678d6d3df78f783abdd705","tid":2133030,"uid":284432,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T18:40:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a9fe0cc04c34bc00fd61d14a12fea9ef3734a78","tid":2133030,"uid":58841,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T18:41:07.000Z","msg":"D傳染者通街走然後報狗要狗隻捉返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c2e88ab9a3c2a2ec8522aa093cb2a3fa06343c6","tid":2133030,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"2a9fe0cc04c34bc00fd61d14a12fea9ef3734a78","tid":2133030,"uid":58841,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T18:41:07.000Z","msg":"D傳染者通街走然後報狗要狗隻捉返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocki